---
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Xiaomi Humanoid - Xi Lin</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 sm:px-10">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-900">Back to home</a>
      <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-mono text-blue-600">Xiaomi Robotics | Robotics Engineer Intern</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Humanoid Motion Retargeting and Skill Simulation</h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-4xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        This experience focused on humanoid robot hardware configuration optimization and simulation systems. I converted factory assembly videos into SMPL trajectories, retargeted complex human motions to humanoids with PHC, and built simulation and low-level policy training loops for assembly-style and payload-related tasks.
      </p>

      <section class="mt-10 rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6 sm:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Program Core</h2>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
          <li>Converted factory assembly videos into SMPL trajectories and retargeted complex human motions to humanoids with PHC, creating a reusable motion dataset for downstream training.</li>
          <li>Built simulation systems and low-level behavior training loops for assembly-style robot tasks, then used Mujoco-side demos to validate the learned motion quality.</li>
          <li>This stage gave me direct engineering experience with retargeting, whole-body control, and practical policy iteration for humanoid skill pipelines.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {["Retargeting", "SMPL", "Mujoco", "WBC", "RL"].map((item) => (
            <span class="rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-white px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">
              {item}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.94fr_1.06fr]">
        <article class="overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4">
          <video controls playsinline class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-black">
            <source src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-sim2sim-demo.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
            Demo
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="grid gap-6">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4">
            <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-overview.png" alt="Retargeting overview" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 object-contain" />
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
              Retargeting
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4">
            <img src="/assets/projects/xiaomi-process.png" alt="Xiaomi process figure" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 object-contain" />
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
              Progress
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
